{"view":"article","slug":"megaminx-megaminx-f2l-s2l","category":"Megaminx","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Megaminx","title":{"en":"Megaminx F2L, S2L Algorithms (First, Second Two Layers)"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/megaminx-megaminx-f2l-s2l/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Megaminx F2L, S2L Algorithms (First, Second Two Layers)</strong></p><p>Cases similar to 3x3 F2L are not shown. Many F2L (S2L) cases are equivalent, in the sense of cube rotation. <strong>F</strong> moves in Megaminx are more fingertrick-friendly and common than F in 3x3. In some situation, <strong>block building</strong> is more convenient than standard F2L. Reduce rotation.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>Free Pair</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/megaminx-megaminx-f2l-s2l/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/megaminx-megaminx-f2l-s2l/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/megaminx-megaminx-f2l-s2l/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/megaminx-megaminx-f2l-s2l/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U R U' R' / R' F R F'\">U R U' R' / R' F R F'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U2 R U2' R' / U2' R U2 R'\">U2 R U2' R' / U2' R U2 R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"F R' F' R / U' F' U F\">F R' F' R / U' F' U F</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U2 F' U2' F / U2' F' U2 F\">U2 F' U2' F / U2' F' U2 F</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(L' R) U2' R\">(L' R) U2' R</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(L R) U2' R\">(L R) U2' R</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/megaminx-megaminx-f2l-s2l/en/imag